<cb:div type="xuzang-notes">
<head>卍續藏 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0572b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0572b09">佛者大覺之稱也如來靈照一彼實相即如來相故淨名以觀自者觀如來相</note>
<note n="0572b10" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0572b10">法身過六情故外入無積</note>
<note n="0572b11" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0572b11">無相之身不以一異自他而觀其體</note>
<note n="0572b12" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0572b12">此岸生死彼岸涅槃中流聖賢也</note>
<note n="0572b13" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0572b13">無相之相何所介其知識</note>
<note n="0572b14" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0572b14">取則失真捨則乖道無相之體覺非覺知非知不可以言意求</note>
<note n="0572b15" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0572b15">如來身名如是觀以斯觀者名為正觀</note>
<note n="0573b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0573b01">沒生二字是發論端</note>
<note n="0573b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0573b02">所得法即無為無相法也</note>
<note n="0573b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0573b03">沒不盡善本沒而非沒生不長諸惡生而非生是無生沒相也</note>
<note n="0573b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0573b04">為不脩淨國及性生者現其剎也不遙現而接來者將顯神力則情悅而悟深耳</note>
<note n="0573b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0573b05">屈尊為難故言乃至樹與華皆能放光明化菩薩作佛事</note>
<note n="0573b06" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0573b06">彼土以寶階嚴飾為遊戲之路故同以往反</note>
<note n="0573b07" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0573b07">陶家輪明就中央下不著地四邊相絕也</note>
<note n="0573b08" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0573b08">重為輕根靜為躁君非三昧力無以得此神通</note>
<note n="0573b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0573b09">行應于內念護于外理會冥感自然之數耳</note>
<note n="0573b10" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0573b10">是人即佛所護念人</note>
<note n="0573b11" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0573b11">前文受記二字得此可以了證</note>
</p>
